<section id="mission" class="section container">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>The objective is to guarantee that everyone has access to the information and resources necessary to make informed sexual health decisions. This involves supporting inclusive education that is free of judgment and based on respect, consent, and equality for everyone.</p>
</section>

<section id="vision" class="section container">
    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
    <p>Our vision is to eliminate barriers such as misinformation, stigma, and prejudice, allowing everyone to make educated decisions about their bodies and relationships in a safe and respectful atmosphere.</p>
